{"tid":1272281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戰士們，黑旗禮已完成，衝立會嘅聲東擊西戰術已成功，想長佔癱瘓立法會應等班賣港賊開會時","createTime":"2019-07-01T10:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T10:33:52.000Z","uid":181531,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"989e112c2dcb13156c17479c87851641ceb39d2c","tid":1272281,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:01:27.000Z","msg":"我知大家因為71係近期最後一次大型聚人嘅機會而感到焦急<br />\n<br />\n但衝入一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得狗冇人嘅立法會</span></span>係唔會有用！<br />\n<br />\n台灣太陽花學運之所以成功、韓國長期佔領之所以迫使總統下台，都係因為佢地係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立法會會期內行動</span></span></strong>！咁先會對港共政權有實質影響！<br />\n<br />\n成功例子在前，我哋點解唔參考一下？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰士們，你哋既然有將生死置諸道外嘅決心，又唔在意和理非民意，使乜急在一時？怕咩到時無人？怕咩唔成功？<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋已經無嘢再輸！但無嘢再輸嘅人永遠立於不敗之地！永遠有翻生嘅機會！<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"68cd1ef3d42ee3cf577eb5d354d5349cec35b0fb","tid":1272281,"uid":34515,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:01:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">轉：立會需要水、頭盔、索帶、遮、first aid、較剪、眼罩<br />\n物資短缺！<br />\n拎去煲底</span></span>"},{"pid":"00f753131b85446b873ba56d77b563942f8ccd55","tid":1272281,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:08:12.000Z","msg":"推到戰士睇到，你鬧我都係咁話"},{"pid":"ef544409176b50189b09b4a90c675d028672295b","tid":1272281,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T10:09:37.000Z","msg":"依家仲係會期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eee306fa7401ea4d2d9b26286e3234d3ee67b335","tid":1272281,"uid":181531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef544409176b50189b09b4a90c675d028672295b","tid":1272281,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyT